snippet.textDisplay:
I do not mean to intend to spark any controversial debate..or a keyboard war but I have a serious thought of why Shiraz Uppal is making the ' Music Occult Symbol" with his left hand during the entire Naat.
Such a shame that he is reciting the praise of the Prophet Muhammed ( ﷺ ) and making the Dajjali sign of the Devil 666.

People may not agree but it's my opinion and I do not like it.
I hope I am wrong  because I don't want such a talented person able to recite the Naat for my Nabi fall into the Trap of the Devil Accursed.
😭
May Allah swt give him Hidayat.

snippet.textDisplay: "Sidra-tul-Muntaha" ( The tree at the extremities of extremes), is a A huge tree on the 7th and highest sky called "Arsh-e-Muala". Its root cover the 6th sky and shades the 7th sky.  From its root 2 rivers of Jannah' (paradise) flow. Beyond the Sidra is the point where no being ever crossed except Prophet Muhammad (S.A.A.W). Even the Arch Angel Gabriel stopped there exclaiming that his 600 wings will burn off by the illumination of the Lord ( Allah). From there on Prophet went on his own to meet Allah during his " Isra-o-Meeraj" (Journey of the Night).
